Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the Millennium Puzzle complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The young boy Yugi Mutou became a master of the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was challenged by a person that has a Millennium Item like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the owner of the Millennium Eye, Pegasus, and went to the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save the soul of Sugoroku, that was stolen by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Together with his friends and with his other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:02:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To remember about the past.... I'm not like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a long dream I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. A terrifying Dark Bakura was in mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way.... there were two Yugis... that was really a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitch Dark Duel!\NCastle of Concealing Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All my Harpies... were defeated...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me all of your Star Chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been disqualified! Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This saves me a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My prey came right to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that brute-looking guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful! He's a Player Killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Duelist hired to take Duelists' Star Chips and kick them off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Player Killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll disqualify you, just as I did this woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disqualified? It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, this is as far as I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't realize my\Ndream of dueling with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losers can shout all they like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:03:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kick his lousy ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't solve the problem even\Nif you beat him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun, Bakura-kun's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take care of the things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat this block-head and get back your Star Chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now on this island, us Player Killers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are searching for Duelists to hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my foremost mission to defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since a suspicious person appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew there would be such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've grown fed up with Pegasus and his ridiculous stunts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, this is the order of the Industrial Illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't give orders for just anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To defeat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great Pegasus-sama feels he doesn't need to waste his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the end of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give these words to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only I can defeat Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just try it while you have the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no chance of beating me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as this darkness exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the darkness falls on this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duelists cannot rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let your guard down for a second, and the darkness will swallow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll suffer the same fate as that woman over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely, block-head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking advantage of people in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the cowardly act of a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, you damn kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you what happens when you try to scar the honor of a Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this duel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wager all six of my Star Chips!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bet all eight of the Star Chips
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stole from that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lack two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use this to make up for the difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be your compensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you lose this duel ,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flames will attack you from the hell of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's going this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you have a rest for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can launch the fire whenever I feel like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ever think of escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the time to joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you don't have to accept these conditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, don't do it Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't even a Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I accept your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will shatter your arrogance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and show you up for what you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See if you {\i1}live{\i0} long enough to beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With your honor as a Duelist on the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you experience the terror of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My card is the Castle of Concealing Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It powers up from the Darkness Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch! The darkness is moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card makes the darkness descend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what'll you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this way
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I cannot even see the cards of\Nmy opponent and the monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great view.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see your side {\i1}very{\i0} well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can see nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Harpies were beaten by this Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you can't gain a power up from the Field Power Source.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, my Dark Monsters can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My darkness will kill your card here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I cannot even see what strategies\Nmy opponent uses in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf Swordsman in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use this card... to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he just play?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf Swordsman was beat down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, that attack is way too low!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to trust Yugi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only do this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are just at your wits' end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To eliminate the darkness of my opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to destroy the Castle of Concealing Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the Defense Power of that castle is 2500.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can be regarded as an invincible air fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have any card in my hand that can beat something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit! What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There must be some strategies for an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn to add a card for another attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call forth a Dark Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's another Dark-type!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still can't see what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, you've already become prey
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and can't run away from the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Predators are waiting to bite you with their fangs in the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't even need to play something stronger than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, isn't there a way to stop him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew that, I wouldn't have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the darkness is overwhelming, counter it with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, I'll try my luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireball Barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can never defeat my monster in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress is blasted apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that it's hard to find the opponent in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Moreover...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}although the light gave me a small glimpse,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the darkness will soon come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I won't be able to see their identities once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am invincible in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you're doing is running away to the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to live, you best learn your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should understand the situation you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is now being grasped in the palm of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the result of this duel as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Now I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know what ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your savage heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just told me how to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bullshit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the sun rises in the day,\Nthe darkness will vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, you'll be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what I'll see at the end of this game...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is a loser dog with his tail between his legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...! Take back what you just said...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a way to beat the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card is my trump.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life ends in five turns!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you what {\i1}true{\i0} darkness is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's not pretending to be confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You;re just trying to bluff your way out of your current situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the darkness on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you try, you have no chance of winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No true Duelist gives up a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when someone else claims they're going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You at least have the pride that most Duelists have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll grant you that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you what my trump card is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sealing Swords of Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Swords... of Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These holy swords have the power to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,block the enemy Monster attacks for three turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they try to hide in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in front of the holy swords of light,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they will be exposed from the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will be trapped in the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having the fate of being destroyed by my card!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way a mere card can destroy my darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have our answer in five turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse of Dragon in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover one more card on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my turn is over with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That card has to be the Sealed Swords of Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only have five turns left!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare look down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn {\i1}brat{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, is it really alright for him to tell his opponent what his card is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this Duel, Yugi is using...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as another form of weapon other than cards to battle the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A weapon other than cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that must be words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Words?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Player Killer is hiding behind the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi can see nothing and his attacks won't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one way to reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His voice... so his words, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun is using his words as a weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his {\i1}true{\i0} trump against the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, show me how you fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a Duelist as stupid as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you regret ever thinking of doing something so foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My card will send that trump card of yours straight to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Card-Hunting Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Card-Hunting Reaper...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll eliminate that set Magic Card you have on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reaper of the Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy his Magic Card, the Sealing Swords of Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yugi!\N-Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card's his trump!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that card's destroyed, Yugi'll be caught by the God of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished once this hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall into hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Card Eraser!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sickle stopped moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not able to attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...say that the Sealing Swords of Light was my trump card...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I never said it was the card I played on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I placed on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was the Hexagram Curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when your Death God attacked this card,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it fell right into my trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you play a Magic or Trap Card,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Card-Hunting Reaper is the thing to watch out for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you had this card in your deck somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's been sealed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can play all the Magic Cards I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to make such judgments, even in that situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he still can't let his guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare deceive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've wasted your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'll really play my trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll set one more Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You set {\i1}two{\i0} Magic Cards on the field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What card is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Facing the despicable attack of the Player Killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi fights the battle with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yugi's got a flame ring set up at his feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous to irritate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sealing Swords of Light can reveal the Monsters on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the chance, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the darkness shows up again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,defeat the enemy with an invincible card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Render the Darkness! The Sealing Swords of Light"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:21:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:22:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
